snippet.title: Welcome to rFactor 2!
snippet.description:
Welcome to rFactor 2, the most diverse and dynamic racing simulation on the planet. Featuring one of the most comprehensive physics engines in simracing, day/night transitions, dynamic weather, esports ready and an ever-growing community. 

Get rFactor 2 today here: http://store.steampowered.com/app/365960/rFactor_2/

Get the DLC here including the GT3 Power Pack and the Formula E Energize Pack: http://store.steampowered.com/itemstore/365960/browse/?filter=Packs

Video concept and creation by Zansho.co.uk
